    Symphony's shoulder was bit by Sinnetwin's head, and now there was a bi=
g chunk ripped out of there.  Hun-Grr's two heads ripped out chunks from Sy=
mphony's left side, and around his back slightly.  And plus, he was still b=
eing burnt by Sinnetwin's back cannon.

     "AAGGGHHHHHHHH!!!!!" He yelled=
 in sheer pain.

     Symphony's body, or what was left of it, was now poor=
ing with mechfluid.  Almost all of his body was burnt badly.  Symphony's le=
ft arm suddenly.......got......ugh.....ripped off......His left arm got bit=
ten right off by Hun-Grr, and now mechfluid was spewing out that side all o=
ver the place.  Soon, if he wasn't careful, his right arm would come off.  =
Symphony dropped his machine gun, his mind slowly went blank.  He fell limp=
.  He went into stasis lock, but was still alive.
